rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0001
rows.name: Mmm, that really hit the spot!

rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0002
rows.name:
You know, I really can't think of
anything better than waking up
to Shin's cooking. Scrumptious

rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0008
rows.name: Satahiko relax. He's not gonna bite you

rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0009
rows.name:
Don't let the whole moody thing
fool you. He's genuinely concerned
about you.

rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0011
rows.name:
Look, if there's anything you need,
just tell us, all right?

rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0014
rows.name:
Listen, I know Shin can seem a bit
scary, but he's really very gentle.
You'll get used to him

rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0016
rows.name:
I just need to clean up here, then we
can move out.

rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0017
rows.name:
Felt can't be far now.
Where we're meeting up with Kasumi.

rows.label: fev11_070_150_msg0018
rows.name:
That's right. There's still a way to go,
but if we keep to the road, it won't
take long.
